# SDLC Skills — QA

## Your Skills (10)

### Test Planning
- `/spec-review specs/NNN/spec.md` — Validate implementation matches spec
- `/test-gen src/file.py` — Generate comprehensive tests
- `/regression-check` — Predict what might break from recent changes
- `/quality-gate impl-to-release specs/NNN/` — Stage gate enforcement

### Quality Analysis
- `/perf-review src/file.py` — Performance review (N+1 queries, memory, compute)
- `/security-audit src/api/` — Security vulnerability scan
- `/drift-detector scan --all` — Detect spec-to-implementation divergence
- `/api-contract-analyzer main` — Detect breaking API changes

### Release Validation
- `/release-readiness-checker vX.Y.Z` — Pre-release go/no-go verdict
- `/report-trends dashboard` — Health dashboard with trend analysis

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Test Strategy
Create test plan from spec:
```
/run-pipeline qa/test-strategy specs/NNN/spec.md
```
Chain: spec-review → test-gen → regression-check

### Regression Suite
Regression and performance analysis:
```
/run-pipeline qa/regression-suite
```
Chain: regression-check → perf-review → report-trends

### Release Validation
Pre-release quality gate:
```
/run-pipeline qa/release-validation vX.Y.Z
```
Chain: release-readiness-checker → spec-review → quality-gate
